products.name: Chelsea Viv' Rangers Metal Buckle Ankle Boots
products.description:
Description & details

The ankle boots are the biggest trend of the season and these Viv' Rangers boots, in a classic Chelsea version, are a real must-have for the autumn season. Hand-crafted in patent leather, this tough girl model is softened by an iconic, metal branded buckle with adorns the front panel, for a decisively elegant twist.

Made in Italy
Women's Roger Vivier Chelsea Viv' Rangers Metal Buckle Ankle Boots
Patent leather upper
Side elastic inserts
Metal buckle with logo
Rear fabric tongue with logo
Leather interior
Rubber outsole
Heel 1 ins
Maintenance and care cards included
Branded dustbag
